.TH "BEEHIIV-POSTS-DELETE" "1" "Apr 2026" "beehiiv-cli" "Beehiiv CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
beehiiv-posts-delete - Delete a post by ID


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbeehiiv posts delete  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Delete post

.PP
Delete or Archive a post. Any post that has been confirmed will have it's status changed to \fBarchived\fR\&. Posts in the \fBdraft\fR status will be permenantly deleted.

.PP
API path: /publications/{publicationId}/posts/{postId}


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for delete

.PP
\fB--query\fP=[]
	Add a repeatable query parameter in key=value form


